As far as I know, this only affected charms cast by PCs on pets that exploited a conflict in code...removing the charm (which *never* gave them an ounce of direct control) would cause pet to go rogue.  Rogue pets would poof due to an earlier sloppy fix.  Only took a year of feedbacks and petitions and emails...<br>
